high_descs: Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the bed on your right.
Pick up pan from the bed.
Head straight towards the floor lamp by turning around and turning left.
anns.task_desc: Examine a pan by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the bed.
Take the pan from the bed.
Turn around and go near the floor lamp.
Put the pan near the lamp and it will be glow.
anns.task_desc: To glow the floor lamp using the pan.

high_descs: Turn left to reach the bed,
Pick up the pan from the left.
Turn around to reach the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the pan under the lamp light.
